Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.17,0:00:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使乃暗夜的鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.75,0:00:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化為罪孽深重的黑色羔羊們的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盲從的白色羔羊們的王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.68,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為世界喚夾暗時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.00,0:00:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.33,0:00:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是光之鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.30,0:00:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是世界的救星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.09,0:00:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撲鼻的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.27,0:01:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀰漫著的血腥味讓腦袋裡都麻木了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.82,0:01:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都染紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.61,0:01:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕陽的照射下 全都一片血紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如此慘絶人寰的景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.12,0:01:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但那是世上絶無僅有的一幅圖畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.22,0:03:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於追上你了 黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.31,0:03:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孕育出人們的不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是不實的虛像嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是攸關我們信仰的重要存在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.45,0:03:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要説那是劍的話 卻過於大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大 寬厚 沉重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.96,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且太粗糙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那簡直就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是獵犬的下場嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聞到血腥味皿奮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人吧這種鬼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夜晚掩蓋的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這世界的畫皮擊穿燒盡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡深植著恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼精彩的地方你怎磨縮起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信徒應該説一句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經遇上奇蹟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多到反胃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 走了 派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.21,0:04:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙果然不是一般人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.64,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是黑色劍士嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你意欲何為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這個魔女不能交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.74,0:05:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以神之正義為名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不畏懼神嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.29,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要妨礙我的神聖使命嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.54,0:05:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼想舔神的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把自己的腦袋獻上如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見到神後替我説一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別來管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.11,0:06:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就來您身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就獨自一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.54,0:06:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個黑色劍士一出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所熟知的世界就開始崩塌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.30,0:06:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破滅了 瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都屏住了呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目光被吸引住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨後察覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追求之物已降臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.10,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非人之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一波未平一波又起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去追黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要捨棄僧籍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.04,0:07:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終究沒能從那無法壓制的黑暗中逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.22,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終 無形的黑暗向我完全展現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像只是不停地害怕下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿新是我的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅一人立於黑暗當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.65,0:08:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那個黑色劍士帶領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來客人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.78,0:08:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後一直拚命在找你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想從我手上想逃沒那麼容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想著抓住我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色劍士大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請允許我加入您的旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.44,0:08:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道 超越了我所深信的秩序的真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.66,0:08:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想學習 能在沒有秩序的黑暗中生存的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.08,0:09:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能做這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚有一天會謝罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺和貴族小姐都那麼誇張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你們的便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那度説
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好乾脆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交代和道歉都不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也幹掉了你們的同伴 彼此彼此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.66,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是指引就算了 我不適合那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你想知道什麼 隨便做就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不妨礙我的事 我也不會説什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.96,0:09:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點奇怪 那個凱茲竟然這麼會乾脆的接受別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.67,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人的話以前的我一定會不由分説拒絶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,説實話這次真是難辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.18,0:10:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然第一次這麼期待別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為自己的不祥而戰慄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被自己的無力所打垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.75,0:10:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最後一次歡笑是什麼時候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了 對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.55,0:10:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走這條路的話要小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是山那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 大爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有山賊出沒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來是出來 但不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是獸鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.73,0:10:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 是山賊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.53,0:10:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樹果嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.18,0:11:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚啊 來了 來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.63,0:11:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被獸鬼襲擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來有五個伙伴的 但是全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也不能就這麼回村裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.02,0:12:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群獸鬼襲擊了村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.06,0:12:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像從故事跑出來的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用傳説對付傳説
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.07,0:12:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想向魔女求救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.29,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是那時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.17,0:12:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是希凱兒 還在修行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是依巴蕾拉 是這孩子的隨從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.39,0:12:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到靈樹之館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有烙印的兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆子 你究竟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.15,0:12:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在先解決那位先生要說的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.28,0:13:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要説的是獸鬼的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒 你把力量借給他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵 當替身啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把每天苦練的成果用於實踐 對你也是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.83,0:13:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.88,0:13:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 能助我這弟子一臂之力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那師傅我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.05,0:13:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願你們受到精靈的庇護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼來了 都來寺院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們了 精靈們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 跑到寺院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 祭司大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 幹掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那個那個人的話 就能從獸鬼手上保護村子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 那傢伙好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂哪邊是怪物了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確不像一般人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.30,0:14:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是那個人在精神能輕易影響物質的狹間彷徨的結果嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是説
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.22,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纏在劍周圍的那個影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼們 都碎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個光輝是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會認同的 那樣的邪術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.33,0:15:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界不僅是在高度和寬度上擴展延伸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.71,0:15:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中也孕育著巨大的深層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.21,0:15:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能以唯一物質論或人的一時興起來論斷世界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接納巨大的謎團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.97,0:15:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在入世之中探求萬事萬物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此即為魔道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個 不得了的小姑娘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.87,0:15:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.63,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然出現了這種怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不創造欞會的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造施展法術的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 司令員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.68,0:16:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等 那傢伙在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經覺得他超乎常人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到已經到如此地步了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣就幹掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.92,0:16:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用魔法只憑自己的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一個人類能達到這個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.81,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須趕緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.43,0:16:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.68,0:16:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比這層幽界更深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個寺院建成之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位於這個山丘的神殿的幽體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.16,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之元素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.70,0:17:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫蒂妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.58,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河水泛濫 朝這邊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.52,0:17:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼 怪物們都被沖走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 我們得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人 魔女大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.74,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.42,0:18:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因奈我沉溺於力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.93,0:18:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.39,0:18:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這度緊張的話 平時做得到的事也會失敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拯救了這個村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.81,0:18:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人會責備你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.86,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這雙眼睛好好看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次相遇對你來説有何意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 待在我身後別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.72,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那把劍的話有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.12,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集成百上千的匚靈的怨念的那把劍的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貫穿她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.38,0:19:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後會有期 可愛的孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好要塌了 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.98,0:19:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在努力中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.02,0:19:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要不行了 抑制不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.91,0:20:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切開空間穿越異層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這把劍的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又説些不知所謂的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼從後面出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.47,0:20:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又欠了人情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向命運抗爭 努力活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後他們相遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.77,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈樹之森的魔女科羅拉致最得意的弟子希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又再一次 這樣認為了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這種靈氣的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.83,0:20:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是洋館的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的結界消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.46,0:20:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有棘手的東西在洋館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼根本不能比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.55,0:20:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.22,0:21:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師 師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯 那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.73,0:21:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.15,0:21:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像希凱兒説的 傷囗裂開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我處理不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.41,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 這樣就算穿上那個也動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.95,0:21:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確 現在這個狀態穿上那個還能保命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還活著喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這是師傅大人的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是不是我的命運 我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.68,0:21:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在能救他的只有我這個魔法師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.27,0:21:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有身為靈樹森林的魔女科羅拉的弟子的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能做到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.77,Preview,,0,0,0,,再見了 我的陽光之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.28,0:24:10.36,Preview,,0,0,0,,人類…那簡直就像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.49,0:24:14.66,Preview,,0,0,0,,使用使徒被授予的力量埋葬黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.74,0:24:18.83,Preview,,0,0,0,,這是你的真正實力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.87,0:24:22.83,Preview,,0,0,0,,這樣才有粉碎的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.56,0:01:31.06,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur3.5\pos(1000,770)}魔女的追憶
